Class NALObjects

    javassist.util.proxy.MethodHandler, Termizer

    public class NALObjects
extends DefaultTermizer
implements Termizer, javassist.util.proxy.MethodHandler
    Dynamic proxy for any POJO that intercepts specific methods and generates reasoner events which can be stored, input to one or more reasoners, etc..
